<p>The winter of 2007/2008 will start on the 22<sup>nd</sup> of
December, 2007, at 1:08 AM EST (December 22<sup>nd</sup> at 6:08 GMT).
It will end (and spring start) on the 20<sup>th</sup> of March, 2008,
at 0:48 AM EST (March 21<sup>st</sup> 5:48 GMT).</p>

<!--
